summaries:
This document is a Form 10-K Annual Report for Oracle Corporation, filed with the United States Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC). The report covers the fiscal year ended on May 31, 2025. The company is registered on the New York Stock Exchange under the ticker symbol ORCL.

The document includes information about the securities registered by Oracle Corporation, such as Common Stock and 3.125% senior notes due July 2025. It also indicates that Oracle Corporation is a large accelerated filer and has filed all required reports for the past 90 days.

Additionally, it mentions that the financial statements included in the filing do not reflect any corrections of errors from previously issued financial statements. The document also includes a reference to Oracle Corporation's definitive proxy statement relating to its 2025 annual meeting of stockholders.
